ing: 1 (12 ounce) can corned beef, cut into chunks
des: "A combination of corned beef, potatoes, and onions. A quick and easy meal."
ins: In a large deep skillet, over medium heat, combine the potatoes, corned beef, onion, and beef broth. Cover and simmer until potatoes are of mashing consistency, and the liquid is almost gone. Mix well, and serve.
